<div id="review_382241847" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/382241847" />
    <a title="Carolyn M" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/11490994-carolyn-m"><img alt="Carolyn M" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_50x66-6a03a5c12233c941481992b82eea8d23.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/382241847?book_show_action=true">Aug 01, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Carolyn M" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Carolyn M" href="/user/show/11490994-carolyn-m">Carolyn M</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>


          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">Everyone</span></div>

        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer382241847" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4435040740887818162">Wow! I love it when a book leaves me unsure about how to describe it. This book is one of those rare cases. Reimagined is an interactive story/guide/reference/experience that introduces you to how your life actually works and the unexpected ways happy people design and live higher quality more satisfying lives. Without spoiling it, it&apos;s nothing you would expect... you actually become part of the story! It&apos;s quite an impressive achievement.<br/><br/>It&apos;s been a long time since I&apos;ve enjoyed a book this much</span>
  <span id="freeText4435040740887818162" style="display:none">Wow! I love it when a book leaves me unsure about how to describe it. This book is one of those rare cases. Reimagined is an interactive story/guide/reference/experience that introduces you to how your life actually works and the unexpected ways happy people design and live higher quality more satisfying lives. Without spoiling it, it's nothing you would expect... you actually become part of the story! It's quite an impressive achievement.<br /><br />It's been a long time since I've enjoyed a book this much - especially a self help book which I don't typically read let alone review. It's written so well and every word, paragraph and anecdote spoke to me. This is hands down the most informative and useful book I've ever read about life and living.</span>
