    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer368189894" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2974686572665135750">I loved this book. This book does a wonderful job of bringing clarity to those things that drive meaningful life experiences and makes the reader a part of the story through insightful questions. The questions profoundly change the experience of this book. This book offers a truly refreshing and intelligent look at life and living that is uniquely valuable. I recommend this book to anyone wanting a better life.</span>

          </span>
