  <span id="freeText4364787265569566948" style="display:none">Simply wonderful. If there's one book everyone should read, this is that book. I read it based on the enthusiastic reviews from others here and ended up purchasing several copies to give away to friends and family as gifts.<br /><br />This book is the definitive owner's manual of life quality. Ian Breck explores those elements that define the life you experience using an interactive approach that makes much of the underlying science transparent but makes you a part of the story. This book offers a refreshing and fascinating experience that's difficult to put down once you begin.<br /><br />If you or someone you know wants to improve the experience and design of your life - even if your life is already pretty wonderful - read this book.</span>
